orld, Apple is offering customers a trade-in deal to encourage customers to recycle old electronics. Through May 16, when customers recycle an eligible piece of tech at an Apple store, they\u0026#39;ll receive 10% off Apple accessories and may be eligible for store credit. A \u003ca href=\"https://www.cnet.com/tech/recycling-tech-survey-2025/\" target=\"_blank\" data-ga-click=\"1\" data-ga-label=\"$text\" data-ga-item=\"text-link\" data-ga-module=\"content_body\" title=\"(opens in a new window)\"\u003enew survey from CNET\u003c/a\u003e (Mashable and CNET are both published by Ziff Davis) found that one in three U.S. adults holds onto old devices simply because they don\u0026#39;t know how to recycle them.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHere are the best Earth Day deals to shop this week. \u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eBest Earth Day tech deals for 2025\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eWhy we like it \u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eEven Apple is \u003ca href=\"https://mashable.com/article/april-17-apple-10-percent-discount-deal\" target=\"_blank\" data-ga-click=\"1\" data-ga-label=\"$text\" data-ga-item=\"text-link\" data-ga-module=\"content_body\"\u003ecelebrating Earth Day\u003c/a\u003e this year by giving customers \u003ca href=\"https://zdcs.link/QbxKJG?pageview_type=Standard\u0026amp;template=article\u0026amp;module=content_body\u0026amp;element=offer\u0026amp;item=text-link\u0026amp;element_label=10%25%20off%20an%20Apple%20accessory\u0026amp;object_type=article\u0026amp;object_uuid=01pYX3CdVhXe1f8sxFsKuj7\u0026amp;short_url=QbxKJG\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmashable.com%2Farticle%2Fapril-21-earth-day-deals\" rel=\"sponsored\" target=\"_blank\" data-ga-click=\"1\" data-ga-label=\"$text\" data-ga-item=\"text-link\" data-ga-module=\"content_body\" title=\"(opens in a new window)\"\u003e10% off an Apple accessory\u003c/a\u003e when they recycle an eligible item in-store. Bonus deal: Apple Watch owners can earn an Earth Day limited-edition award by completing any 30-minute workout o